      "height": 300,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Next Steps\n\n### Near-Term\n- ‚úÖ Standardize `.node` format on `fileVersion: \"1.0\"`\n- ‚úÖ Enforce safe delta mutations (reject unsafe full rewrites)\n- üîÑ Improve auto-layout so minimal payloads look professional\n- üîÑ Formalize document URL semantics\n\n### Medium-Term\n- Publish explicit command schema for AI integrations\n- Template gallery + community sharing\n- Read-only embed viewer\n- Plugin marketplace\n\n### Long-Term\n- Real-time collaboration\n- Execution runtime for workflow graphs\n- Agent SDK for building on Twilite"
